{"tid":1491554,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung Galaxy 集中討論區（57）","createTime":"2019-08-20T12:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T12:58:04.000Z","uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b4c5b389dfee82b23d55843632f36152da026153","tid":1491554,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:58:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Samsung Galaxy Note 10/Note 10+</span> 香港版將會在 <ins>8 月 23 日</ins>正式推出<strong>幻光</strong>、<strong>幻黑</strong>與<strong>幻白</strong>三個版本。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/IMG_20190807_073712.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilemagazinehk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2FIMG_20190807_073712.jpg&h=fb5362f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGalaxy Note 10 除了幻黑﹑幻白及幻光外，還有<strong>藍</strong>﹑<strong>紅</strong>、<strong>粉紅</strong>三色，不過可惜這三款顏色都唔會在香港推出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/IMG_20190808_062706-800x500_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilemagazinehk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2FIMG_20190808_062706-800x500_c.jpg&h=b525104f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}